    "- The purpose of the pipeline is to assemble several steps that can be cross-validated together while setting different parameters. \n",
    "- For this, it enables setting parameters of the various steps using their names and the parameter name separated by a ‘__’.\n",
    "- List of (name, transform) tuples that are chained, in the order in which they are chained, with the last object an estimator.\n",
    "- param_grid: list of dictionaries, [{key1:[val1, val2], key2:[val1, val2]}, \n",
    "    {key1:[val1, val2], key2:[val1, val2]}]"
